com.blukii.sdk.config

Interface DataManager.OnAssignBlukiiListener

  • Enclosing class:
    DataManager

    public static interface DataManager.OnAssignBlukiiListener

    The listener interface for receiving state changes from assigning blukiis to a user in blukii cloud. Implementations of this interface get notified when the assignment is done or an error occurred while assigning blukiis to a user in blukii cloud.
